Does a talent marketplace exist to hire engineers for one-off small dev tasks or script writing?<p>Think projects along the lines of...
- &quot;write a node script the connect to the Google Calendar API and return all meetings next week as a CSV&quot;
- &quot;make a jupyter notebook to return the standard deviation of a column in a csv&quot;
- &quot;write a script to connect to the Spotify API and save all followed artists to a plain text file&quot;<p>In other words, a marketplace for things most engineers could do given the time but just want delivered faster without having to tinker at it. I know a large part of the delivery on Upwork is the follow through and iterative designs, but this would be more along the lines of one-and-done delivery.
